      • extractMapFeature

        public MapFeature extractMapFeature(Set<String> varIds,
                                    RegularGrid targetGrid,
                                    Double elevation,
                                    org.joda.time.DateTime time)
                             throws DataReadingException
        Extracts a MapFeature from this GridFeature
        Parameters:
        varIds - The variable IDs to extract. If null, all variables are extracted.
        targetGrid - The desired RegularGrid of the resulting MapFeature
        elevation - The elevation at which to extract data, can be null only if this GridFeature has no vertical domain
        time - The time at which to extract data, can be null only if this GridFeature has no vertical domain
        Returns:
        The extracted MapFeature
        Throws:
        DataReadingException - If there is a problem reading the required data
